name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Gitnu - Git interactive terminal not unix

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An interative terminal for Git in Chrome

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A Git terminal client Chrome App by Cam Fitzgerald (camandco.com)

Current functionality includes:
- terminal operations
- git clone
- git log (with paging)
- git status
- git commit
- git branch
- git checkout
- git push (currently only for master)

Run help to see implemented keyboard shortcuts (emacs style).

Note- git commit always commits -a and will commit untracked files.

Other functions are partially implemented but may fail. Do not use for data that is not backed up.
